  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Aspects </strong><em>beast</em>, <em>blood</em></p><hr /><p>From time to time, a vampire will willingly share their blood with an animal to bind the beast to their whims - much more rarely, a vampire or dhampir might do so to save the life of the animal, and forms a mutual bond of respect, or even love, with them.</p><p>Legend tells of a dhampir warrior clad in a suit of armor and sword crafted by a loving parent, and her frightening skill.</p><hr /><p><strong>Set Items: </strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.XFUrBQzcEItHxIvE]{Scarlet Blade Sword (level 1)}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.RD4C9XMaEWdz1wZa]{+1 Scarlet Blade Armor (level 5)}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.zwf8ed2W60xImUcQ]{Barding of the Bloodwolf}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.WdNSWpJea8moQ2Fs]{Wilting Rose (Greater)}, @UUID[Actor.Sk0x5dGjX1LuSDjq.Item.n38iig05RNTRlBUb]{Ró Sálna, the Unbound Heart}</p><hr /><p><strong>Gifts: </strong>The set grants the following gifts.</p><ul><li><p><em>1</em>:<em> </em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.lKZU9tOHWLHPVjdu]{Pack Mentality}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.gyTzMaxXvEYhtMyp]{Beast Senses}</p></li><li><p><em>2</em>:<em> </em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.Datsqxq2DDoNlJgb]{Resilient Blood}</p></li><li><p><em>3</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.c8C9bQeVCdkx0vxr]{Pack Stance}</p></li><li><p><em>4</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.eYRGBUO2ZyB21omt]{Lifeblood}</p></li><li><p><em>5</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.awNdjnwzKUE1vr7u]{Field of Blood}</p></li></ul><hr /><p><strong>Collective Features: </strong>The set grants the following features.</p><ul><li><p><em>Two Items</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.R9BWPro2LC6cLvht]{Pack Mentality} requires <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> instead of <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span>.</p></li><li><p><em>Three Items</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.1BBNOe6BggOeDvGI]{Pack Mentality} can be used twice a day. The AC from @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.Datsqxq2DDoNlJgb]{Resilient Blood} becomes +2, and the resistance equals the relic's level.</p></li><li><p><em>Four Items</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.80tp7Zzf3vzpCR4t]{Pack Mentality} becomes a <span class=\"action-glyph\">f,</span> with the trigger of rolling initiative, and can be used at will. @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.Datsqxq2DDoNlJgb]{Resilient Blood} gains resistance to all physical damage equal to half your level.</p></li><li><p><em>Five Items</em>: The frequency of Blood Pack on your companion's @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.zwf8ed2W60xImUcQ]{Barding of the Bloodwolf} becomes once per hour.</p></li></ul>"
    },
